{"tid":1450389,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：請將今晚發生的地獄慘劇，傳給美國負責制訂《香港人權及民主法案》的議員看，並請求他們盡快召開會議審議。","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:46:54.000Z","uid":107060,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f18bfb2f162ed68483740dc7ff5bb8ad2b78532","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"陳雲：請將今晚發生的地獄慘劇，傳給美國負責制訂《香港人權及民主法案》的議員看，並請求他們盡快召開會議審議。<br />\n其他，大家忍著。我可以安靜忍著，你們也可以吧。<br />\n我幾乎進入涅磐狀態的安靜。人間本該是這樣的，因為有我們在，人間就是這樣。我們不是無辜的。我們是苦的因。"},{"pid":"9f4a5d89d3bac35efe0e5ddccc195e65cdaf30a2","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17f9b35bd98decc87e63a1e6aeaf4f72ed7571c","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe486e5f1dad36df3915bcadf5e57dd62024ec2c","tid":1450389,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1c5473a05a56e99167ec966ba56d898301a5df","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95f7223fd94a3d02ba9b2a18e02626d7364d7c9","tid":1450389,"uid":265429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"陳雲：很多人不明白，我們面對的是一個專政體系（totalitarian regime）。我與這個源自蘇維埃的專政體系，周旋了三十幾年。各位不信我的，結果有今日。<br />\n源自前蘇聯的俄羅斯外交部發言之後，香港就出現昨晚的血腥鎮壓，港共政府露出蘇維埃政府的本性。莫斯科的蘇維埃與北京的蘇維埃合流，令香港人見識清楚，我們面對的是一個專政體系。<br />\n我曾經帶你們見到真相的，也曾經帶你們如何在安全的環境完成香港自治。<br />\n香港是西柏林，我們站在自由民主憲政那邊。但請你老實認識清楚，我們面對的是一個蘇維埃政權（soviet regime）。而香港人背棄過我的鬥爭方法，至今仍在誣衊我。<br />\n潛伏。讀書是武裝思想，也是靈性救贖。請各位讀好《香港城邦論》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/commerce/products/1537897132904577/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcommerce%2Fproducts%2F1537897132904577%2F&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvjX0Nqj3uEASyejP0bzfnYY%3D&h=f7f128f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/commerce/products/1537897132904577/</a>"},{"pid":"2b890fe54a6f3c184cbfe2d2a7175a9abc3d8489","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a9c1be179dcc44935e959da60c9f550a45619d","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d105c18fd7b70e785230a06241a83bcb458abff7","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604787666542e89db02f76a04d857358da2c0fa7","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbfdf6e49ba69b4268eef4bee01ad7edfdf720f","tid":1450389,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e10a8f2c92a73c1c79f7e0b306ad51d6079882","tid":1450389,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:46:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}